<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>设备域新人开发指南 · 结合 AI</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --soft: #64748b;
      --border: #cbd5e1;
      --border-soft: #e2e8f0;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --ok: #059669;
      --ok-soft: #ecfdf5;
      --warn: #b45309;
      --warn-soft: #fffbeb;
      --danger: #b91c1c;
      --danger-soft: #fef2f2;
      --info: #0369a1;
      --info-soft: #f0f9ff;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    code, kbd {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", "Consolas", "Menlo", monospace;
      font-size: 0.92em;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: #3730a3;
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 24px 72px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px 28px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero .eyebrow {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .hero p.lead {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .hero .meta {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--soft);
    }

    .toc {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .toc a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      transition: all 0.15s ease;
    }

    .toc a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 22px 26px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      scroll-margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .card h2 .num {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 18px 0 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card p, .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14.5px;
    }

    .card ul, .card ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .card li {
      margin: 4px 0;
    }

    .card-intro {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14.5px;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    table.grid {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    table.grid th, table.grid td {
      padding: 9px 12px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    table.grid th {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      background: #fafbff;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    table.grid td code {
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .group-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin: 18px 0 8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ========== 工具分组（可折叠） ========== */
    details.tool-group {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fdfdff;
      margin: 14px 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    details.tool-group + details.tool-group {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    details.tool-group > summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: background 0.15s ease;
    }
    details.tool-group > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    details.tool-group > summary::marker { content: ""; }
    details.tool-group[open] > summary {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }
    details.tool-group > summary:hover { background: #eef2f7; }
    details.tool-group > summary .gt-title {
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    details.tool-group > summary .gt-count {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--soft);
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-left: 6px;
      text-transform: none;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    details.tool-group > summary .chev {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-right: 2px solid var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--muted);
      transform: rotate(-45deg);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    details.tool-group[open] > summary .chev {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
    details.tool-group .tg-body {
      padding: 12px 14px 14px;
    }
    details.tool-group .tg-body > :first-child { margin-top: 0; }
    details.tool-group .tg-body > :last-child  { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .tree {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", "Consolas", monospace;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      background: #fafbff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      color: var(--text);
      white-space: pre;
      overflow-x: auto;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .tree .comment { color: var(--soft); }
    .tree .key { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

    .callout {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      border-left: 3px solid;
    }

    .callout.ok {
      background: var(--ok-soft);
      border-color: var(--ok);
      color: #065f46;
    }

    .callout.warn {
      background: var(--warn-soft);
      border-color: var(--warn);
      color: #78350f;
    }

    .callout.danger {
      background: var(--danger-soft);
      border-color: var(--danger);
      color: #7f1d1d;
    }

    .callout.info {
      background: var(--info-soft);
      border-color: var(--info);
      color: #0c4a6e;
    }

    .callout strong { color: inherit; }
    .callout code { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

    /* ========== 阶段卡（核心流程专用） ========== */
    .phase-group {
      margin: 16px 0 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .phase-group .dot {
      width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .phase-group.pre .dot   { background: #3b82f6; }
    .phase-group.code .dot  { background: #059669; }
    .phase-group.post .dot  { background: #7c3aed; }
    .phase-group.wrap .dot  { background: #64748b; }
    .phase-group.pre   { color: #1d4ed8; }
    .phase-group.code  { color: #047857; }
    .phase-group.post  { color: #6d28d9; }
    .phase-group.wrap  { color: #334155; }

    details.stage {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fdfdff;
      margin: 10px 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    details.stage.pre  { border-left-color: #3b82f6; }
    details.stage.code { border-left-color: #059669; }
    details.stage.post { border-left-color: #7c3aed; }
    details.stage.wrap { border-left-color: #64748b; }

    details.stage > summary {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      align-items: center;
      list-style: none;
      user-select: none;
    }
    details.stage > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    details.stage > summary::marker { display: none; }
    details.stage > summary:hover {
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.04);
    }
    details.stage[open] > summary {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    details.stage .idx {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    details.stage.pre  .idx { color: #3b82f6; }
    details.stage.code .idx { color: #059669; }
    details.stage.post .idx { color: #7c3aed; }
    details.stage.wrap .idx { color: #64748b; }

    details.stage .head h3 {
      margin: 0 0 2px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    details.stage .head .sub {
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--soft);
    }

    details.stage .chev {
      color: var(--soft);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }
    details.stage[open] .chev {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    details.stage .expand {
      padding: 12px 16px 14px 110px;
      background: #fdfdff;
    }

    /* 展开/收起 全部按钮 */
    .phase-tools {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 12px 0 4px;
    }
    .phase-btn {
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      background: var(--panel);
      color: var(--muted);
      border-radius: 999px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.15s ease;
    }
    .phase-btn:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .io {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
      gap: 8px 10px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      margin: 3px 0;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .io .tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .io .tag.in   { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
    .io .tag.do   { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .io .tag.out  { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
    .io .tag.done { background: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; }
    .io .val { color: var(--muted); }
    .io .val code { font-size: 0.88em; }

    /* ========== 工具速查表 ========== */
    table.lookup { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0; }
    table.lookup th, table.lookup td {
      padding: 9px 12px; text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    table.lookup th { background: #fafbff; font-size: 13px; }
    table.lookup td.scene { width: 40%; }
    table.lookup td.tool  { width: 30%; }
    table.lookup td.note  { color: var(--soft); font-size: 13px; }
    table.lookup td code { white-space: nowrap; }

    /* ========== 流程图（核心流程总览） ========== */
    .flow-chart {
      margin: 14px 0;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fdfdff;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .flow-chart svg {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 760px;
      height: auto;
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .flow-chart .node { cursor: pointer; }
    .flow-chart .node rect {
      stroke-width: 1.5;
      transition: filter 0.15s ease, stroke-width 0.15s ease;
    }
    .flow-chart .node:hover rect,
    .flow-chart .node:focus-visible rect {
      filter: brightness(0.96);
      stroke-width: 2.5;
    }
    .flow-chart .node-idx {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-anchor: middle;
    }
    .flow-chart .node-name {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      text-anchor: middle;
      fill: #334155;
    }
    .flow-chart .lane-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .flow-chart .lane-label.pre   { fill: #1d4ed8; }
    .flow-chart .lane-label.code  { fill: #047857; }
    .flow-chart .lane-label.post  { fill: #6d28d9; }
    .flow-chart .lane-label.wrap  { fill: #334155; }
    .flow-chart .node.pre  rect   { fill: #eff6ff; stroke: #3b82f6; }
    .flow-chart .node.code rect   { fill: #ecfdf5; stroke: #059669; }
    .flow-chart .node.post rect   { fill: #f5f3ff; stroke: #7c3aed; }
    .flow-chart .node.wrap rect   { fill: #f1f5f9; stroke: #64748b; }
    .flow-chart .node.pre  .node-idx  { fill: #1d4ed8; }
    .flow-chart .node.code .node-idx  { fill: #047857; }
    .flow-chart .node.post .node-idx  { fill: #6d28d9; }
    .flow-chart .node.wrap .node-idx  { fill: #334155; }
    .flow-chart .flow-edge {
      stroke: #94a3b8;
      stroke-width: 1.5;
      fill: none;
    }
    .flow-chart .flow-edge.fail {
      stroke: #f59e0b;
      stroke-dasharray: 5 4;
      stroke-width: 1.3;
    }
    .flow-chart .flow-legend {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: var(--soft);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .flow-chart .flow-legend .swatch {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-right: 5px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .flow-chart .flow-legend .line {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 22px;
      height: 0;
      border-top: 1.5px dashed #f59e0b;
      vertical-align: middle;
      margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .flow-chart .flow-legend .spacer { flex: 1; }

    /* ========== 知识分层卡（可折叠） ========== */
    details.kb-layer {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      background: #fdfdff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    details.kb-layer > summary {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      user-select: none;
    }
    details.kb-layer > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    details.kb-layer > summary::marker { display: none; }
    details.kb-layer > summary:hover {
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.04);
    }
    details.kb-layer[open] > summary {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }
    details.kb-layer > summary h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    details.kb-layer > summary .badge {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    details.kb-layer > summary .chev {
      color: var(--soft);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }
    details.kb-layer[open] > summary .chev {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    details.kb-layer .kb-body {
      padding: 12px 18px 16px;
    }
    details.kb-layer .kb-body .kb-desc {
      color: var(--soft);
      font-size: 13.5px;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    /* ========== 双列红绿清单 ========== */
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .two-col .col {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .two-col .col.red    { border-color: #fecaca; background: var(--danger-soft); }
    .two-col .col.green  { border-color: #bbf7d0; background: var(--ok-soft); }
    .two-col .col h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .two-col .col.red h3   { color: var(--danger); }
    .two-col .col.green h3 { color: var(--ok); }
    .two-col .col ul { margin: 6px 0 0; padding-left: 18px; }
    .two-col .col li { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text); }

    /* ========== Tip ========== */
    .tip {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--soft);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .tip strong { color: var(--text); }

    .foot {
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--soft);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .foot code { background: transparent; color: var(--soft); }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .hero { padding: 20px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 22px; }
      .card { padding: 18px; }
      details.stage > summary { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr auto; padding: 12px 14px; }
      details.stage .idx { font-size: 20px; }
      details.stage .expand { padding: 10px 14px 12px 74px; }
      .io { grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr; }
      .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      table.lookup td.scene,
      table.lookup td.tool { width: auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">

    <header class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">openspec/docs/device · 新人指南</div>
      <h1>设备域新人开发指南 · 结合 AI</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        面向第一次在设备域做开发的同学。目标：<strong>看懂一次完整开发要走哪些阶段、每一步拿什么进、产出什么出去、该用哪个工具、去哪查资料</strong>。
      </p>
      <div class="meta">
        本文路径：<code>openspec/docs/device/设备域新人开发指南</code>（HTML，无扩展名）
        · 配合阅读：<code>openspec/docs/device/readme食用指南.md</code>、<code>openspec/docs/device/开发流程.md</code>
      </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="toc">
      <a href="#core">1. 核心流程</a>
      <a href="#tools">2. 选择合适的工具</a>
      <a href="#kb">3. 相关知识目录</a>
      <a href="#setup">附 A. 一次性准备</a>
      <a href="#safety">附 B. 安全红线</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="callout info">
      <strong>怎么用这份文档：</strong>
      第一次读 —— 从头到尾过一遍，对 <strong>核心流程</strong> 的 12 个阶段建立心智模型；
      之后做任务 —— 遇到卡点直接跳 <strong>选择合适的工具</strong>；
      要深挖 —— 去 <strong>相关知识目录</strong> 找对应入口。
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- 1. 核心流程 -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <section id="core" class="card">
      <h2><span class="num">01</span>核心流程 · 每个阶段的输入与输出</h2>
      <p class="card-intro">
        一次完整的设备域开发从"拿到任务"到"change 合入并回写"分 12 个阶段。
        每个阶段给出 <strong>输入（IN）</strong>、<strong>动作（DO）</strong>、
        <strong>输出（OUT）</strong>、<strong>完成标志（DONE）</strong>。
        只有当前阶段 DONE 才进入下一个，避免把锅藏到后面。
      </p>

      <div class="callout ok">
        <strong>分工约定：</strong>
        每一阶段的 DO 行都会标明执行方 ——
        <code>人</code>：你亲自决策或下判断；
        <code>AI</code>：Cursor Agent 按技能执行；
        <code>人+AI</code>：协作完成，AI 出草稿，你过目定稿。
      </div>

      <div class="flow-chart" aria-label="核心流程总览图">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1020 480" role="img" aria-labelledby="flow-title flow-desc">
          <title id="flow-title">设备域开发 12 阶段流程总览</title>
          <desc id="flow-desc">从"进入上下文"到"周期收尾"共 12 个阶段，按开发前 / 编码 / 开发后 / 收尾分 4 个泳道。任一阶段 DONE 不达标均可回退到上游阶段。</desc>
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrow-flow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" orient="auto-start-reverse">
