      <details class="stage pre">
        <summary>
          <span class="idx">01</span>
          <div class="head">
            <h3>进入设备上下文</h3>
            <div class="sub">技能：<code>device-context-entry</code></div>
          </div>
          <span class="chev">▸</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="expand">
          <div class="io"><span class="tag in">IN</span>  <span class="val">一条任务描述（口头需求 / Jira 链接 / bug 现象）</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag do">DO</span>  <span class="val"><code>AI</code> 校验设备 profile 是否启用——任一成立即生效：<code>.ai-context/switch.json</code>（或 <code>openspec/ai-context/switch.json</code>）中 <code>deviceDevelopProfile: true</code>、环境变量 <code>STUDIO_AI_DEVICE_ENTRY=true/1/on</code>、用户显式要求；启用后按 <code>profiles/device/entry.md</code> 的 load-order 加载设备规则与技能</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag out">OUT</span> <span class="val">已装入设备 profile 的对话上下文 + 任务归属的问题域初判</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag done">DONE</span><span class="val">AI 能引用 <code>openspec/docs/device/</code> 中的规则与技能名称作答，不再泛泛回答</span></div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="stage pre">
        <summary>
          <span class="idx">02</span>
          <div class="head">
            <h3>明确需求与方案</h3>
            <div class="sub">技能：<code>device-jira-analyze</code>（有 Jira 时）/ <code>device-problem-analysis</code>（只有现象时）</div>
          </div>
          <span class="chev">▸</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="expand">
          <div class="io"><span class="tag in">IN</span>  <span class="val">Jira issue URL 或 bug 复现现象；明确的业务目标</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag do">DO</span>  <span class="val"><code>AI</code> 抓取 Jira / 整理现象，结合 <code>openspec/specs/device/主题索引.md</code> 给出分析；<code>人</code> 判定取舍</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag out">OUT</span> <span class="val">候选代码入口 · 可能根因 · 最小改动路径 · 风险点 · 验证建议</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag done">DONE</span><span class="val">方案你能用 3 句话讲清楚，且确定了改哪些文件、不改哪些</span></div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="stage pre">
        <summary>
          <span class="idx">03</span>
          <div class="head">
            <h3>检索背景资料</h3>
            <div class="sub">技能：<code>device-knowledge-search</code></div>
          </div>
          <span class="chev">▸</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="expand">
          <div class="io"><span class="tag in">IN</span>  <span class="val">阶段 02 得到的问题域关键词 / 候选模块名</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag do">DO</span>  <span class="val"><code>AI</code> 先查 <code>openspec/specs/device/主题索引.md</code> 与 <code>openspec/specs/device/来源映射表.md</code>，再用 <code>Glob</code> / <code>rg</code> / <code>SemanticSearch</code> 进入源码</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag out">OUT</span> <span class="val">相关架构文档 · OpenSpec 变更 · 源码入口的引用清单</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag done">DONE</span><span class="val">能回答「为什么现状是这样」「改了会影响谁」两个问题</span></div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 编码 -->
      <div class="phase-group code"><span class="dot"></span>编码 · 实现与本地验证</div>

      <details class="stage code">
        <summary>
          <span class="idx">04</span>
          <div class="head">
            <h3>设计与编码</h3>
            <div class="sub">无专属技能 · <code>人+AI</code> 协作</div>
          </div>
          <span class="chev">▸</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="expand">
          <div class="io"><span class="tag in">IN</span>  <span class="val">阶段 02/03 产出的方案 + 代码入口</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag do">DO</span>  <span class="val"><code>人</code> 定模块边界与接口；<code>AI</code> 按 <em>最小化格式改动</em> 落地；<code>人</code> 每次接受前读一遍 diff</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag out">OUT</span> <span class="val">未提交的代码 diff（功能代码 + 必要注释）</span></div>
          <div class="io"><span class="tag done">DONE</span><span class="val">代码可编译、无明显越界改动、逻辑你讲得出来</span></div>
        </div>
      </details>

